I-NFP ifunga iyagomela ukuthi izolinqoba ukhetho lwezindawo kuMasipala waseNquthu.Ibamba likaSihlalo weNFP kuzwelonke, uMnuz Bheki Gumbi uthe bazimisele ngokulinqoba ukhetho lwaseNquthu kumnyama kubomvu.&quot;Uma singanqobanga ithina esizobeka inkosi kumkhandlu waseNquthu,&quot; kusho uGumbi.Uthe bazolungenela kuwona wonke ama-ward angu-17, ukhetho lwaseNquthu njengoba ngeledlule, uNgqongqoshe wezokuBusa ngokuBambisana neziNdaba zoMdabu KwaZulu-Natal uNkk Nomusa Dube-Ncube esifundazweni ehlakaze umkhandlu wathi kumele kuqalwe phansi ukhetho.